brief_summary.textblock:
      Primary Objective:

      To assess efficacy aflibercept + 5-fluorouracil (5-FU)/levofolinate/irinotecan (FOLFIRI) by
      objective response rate (ORR).

      Secondary Objective:

      To assess the following:

        -  safety profile;

        -  progression free survival (PFS);

        -  overall survival (OS);

        -  pharmacokinetics (PK);

        -  immunogenicity.
